column6: At the end of the world is a man, Namor, King of Atlantis! But Atlantis is not under the sea in 1602. With both Doom and the Four from the Fantastick at his doorstep, what will King Namor do?
column8: | penciller:Pascal Alixe | writer:Peter David | penciller (cover):Gabriele Dell'Otto | letterer:Todd Klein | inker:John Livesay | colorist:Rob Schwager
